                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7795" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0305</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1922 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信创正当时，协同共发展：X公司的流程管理升级之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovation is in Progress, Collaboration Promotes Development: The Path of Process Management Upgrade at Company X</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">葛淳棉，邓慧琪，姜军辉（通讯作者），陈倚倩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华南理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">X公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">27 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信创；跨部门协同；流程活动改善；流程优化；流程再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Information technology application innovation; Cross-departmental collaboration; Business process activity improvement; Business process improvement; Business process reengineering</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着信创战略布局的全面推进和国产替代需求的集中爆发，X公司迎来了历史性的发展机遇，但也面临着业务拓展、客户升级带来的诸多流程管理挑战。尽管X公司采取了一系列战略转型与组织结构调整措施，但内部资源配置失衡、前后端协同工作矛盾、项目紧急安全事故仍频频发生，X公司深陷流程之困，破解前端销售、产品研发、技术专家间的跨部门协同矛盾迫在眉睫。然而，组织结构的调整无法一蹴而就，业务流程的优化也不能一步到位，X公司应该如何实现业务流程升级？本案例描述了X公司通过调整组织结构，改善业务流程活动，开展流程优化项目，启动流程再造计划，并运用相关的流程管理措施，逐步解决在跨部门需求沟通、需求分析和上线维保过程中暴露的流程漏洞，实现流程管理升级的过程。本案例有助于引导学员深入思考企业建立流程管理持续优化机制的重要性，并为企业在内外部环境变化情境下开展流程管理工作提供经验参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the comprehensive promotion of the strategic layout of information technology application innovation and the concentrated outbreak of domestic substitution demand, Company X has encountered a historic opportunity for development. However, it is also confronted with numerous challenges in business expansion and customer upgrades, which bring about various dilemmas in process management. Despite implementing a series of strategic transformations and organizational restructuring measures, Company X continues to grapple with internal resources misallocation, conflicts in front-end collaboration, and frequent occurrences of urgent security incidents. Company X finds itself trapped in the quagmire of process management, urgently seeking to resolve interdepartmental collaboration conflicts among sales teams, developers, and technical experts. It is not possible to address these issues through a one-step solution of organizational restructuring, nor is it feasible to achieve instant improvement of business processes. How, then, can Company X upgrade its business processes? This case describes how Company X, gradually resolves the process issues exposed during interdepartmental processes of technical communication, requirement analysis, as well as deployment and maintenance through adjusting its organizational structure, improving business process activities, initiating business process improvement projects, launching business process reengineering plans, and applying relevant process management methods, finally achieving an upgrade in business process management. This case aims to guide students to reflect on the importance of establishing a continuous improvement mechanism for process management within enterprises, while also providing practical insights for conducting process management work in the face of internal environmental changes.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《流程管理》、《现代企业管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务流程如何应对内外部环境变化；业务流程管理与组织结构调整的关系；基于流程的组织结构调整；流程活动改善概念；STRST流程活动改善方法；ECERA流程活动优化方法；流程优化概念及内容；流程管理团队与流程优化小组；流程分级分类；流程再造的概念与核心内容；流程管理升级的层级与对比；流程的长效运行机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
